data.description: Phase 4 Selling Now! Set your sights on an unparalleled quality of living. Introducing phase four of Agua Estates, a stunning ninety-five home community by Contempo Builder. Conveniently located within minutes of the world renowned Houston Medical Center, Hermann Park, Museum District and more. Once inside the gate, enjoy a lap around the jogging trail or take a walk to our dog park. Homeowners will have the option of two distinct floor plans featuring first floor living, private driveways and spacious backyards. Stop by our model home and fall in love with everything that Agua has to offer. Tour our Model Home located at 4409 Abaco Ln, Wednesday - Friday 10:30am - 6:30pm, Saturday 11:00pm - 6:00pm & Sunday 11:00pm - 5:00pm.
